ЁЯФБ What is GitOps? тАУ DVAO Principle
English:

GitOps follows DVAO:

D тАУ Declarative: System state is defined in YAML files

V тАУ Versioned: Everything is stored in Git

A тАУ Automated: Changes are auto-applied

O тАУ Observed: System continuously checks actual vs desired state

